    <item>
      <title>《华尔街日报》称，马斯克的吸毒行为令特斯拉和 SpaceX 领导人担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/elon-musk-s-drug-use-concerns-tesla-spacex-leaders-wsj-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》援引熟悉这位亿万富翁和公司情况的未透露姓名人士的消息报道，埃隆·马斯克的吸毒行为令他所经营企业的高管和董事会成员感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/elon-musk-s-drug-use-concerns-tesla-spacex-leaders-wsj-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:14:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国国务委员会建议反对数字钱包计划：The Nation</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/thai-council-of-state-advises-against-digital-wallet-program-the-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《国家报》报道，泰国国务委员会办公室将提出法律意见，认为总理斯雷塔·塔维信 (Srettha Thavisin) 政府不能通过立法为 5000 亿泰铢（144 亿美元）的数字钱包计划提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/thai-council-of-state-advises-against-digital-wallet-program-the-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于市场持续疲软，沙特阿拉伯下调亚洲石油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/saudi-arabia-cuts-oil-prices-to-asia-as-market-weakness-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场持续疲软，沙特阿拉伯将下调 2 月份所有地区（包括其主要亚洲市场）买家的主要原油价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/saudi-arabia-cuts-oil-prices-to-asia-as-market-weakness-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:39:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sole 表示，CVC 即将从 Permira 手中收购 La Piadineria</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/cvc-nears-acquisition-of-la-piadineria-from-permira-sole-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《Il Sole 24 Ore》报道，CVC Capital Partners 即将从 Permira 手中收购意大利连锁餐厅 Gruppo La Piadineria，但未透露该信息的来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-07/cvc-nears-acquisition-of-la-piadineria-from-permira-sole-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
